Place the lamb, lemon rind and juice, rosemary and peppers in a non-metallic bowl and stir well. Cover and leave to marinate in a cool place for 30 minutes.Meanwhile, put the hummus ingredients in a food processor or blender and blitz for 30 seconds. Place in a bowl.Heat a griddle or heavy-based frying pan, add the lamb mixture and the aubergine and fry for 3â€”4 minutes, or until the lamb is cooked through (You may need to do this in batches.).Heat the tortillas. Wrap the lamb and vegetables in the tortillas with the hummus and serve rocket.